title: United Kingdom Imports of Non-eu
description: Imports of Non-eu in the United Kingdom increased to 30117.18 GBP Million in September from 29975 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Non-eu in the United Kingdom averaged 14660.08 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 32101.84 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 6377.65 GBP Million in December of 1996. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Non-eu.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
